OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1782118104
OL,3,CPeston: Starmer could announce delayed
OL,4,Cdeparture to stay in post until
OL,5,CSeptember
OL,7,FI am told that the PM has not yet
OL,8,Fdefinitively decided that he will
OL,9,Fannounce his departure. "It is looking
OL,10,Fthat way," says a source, "but it is
OL,11,Fnot 100%."
OL,13,FThe prediction, among Keir Starmer's
OL,14,Fclose colleagues, is that he will
OL,15,Fdecide to stay in post until just
OL,16,Fbefore the Labour conference in late
OL,17,FSeptember.
OL,19,F"In those circumstances of a delayed
OL,20,Fexit, history will probably be kinder
OL,21,Fto him," said a colleague.
OL,26,@qD@YOUrD@JO]rD@[OUsD@JO]{D@AOU}D@HO]
