OL,3,CPeston: Starmer could announce delayed
OL,4,Cdeparture to stay in post until
OL,5,CSeptember
OL,7,F"But of course we understand the
OL,8,Finstinct just to have done with it and
OL,9,Fwalk away."
OL,11,FAs for the timing of any such
OL,12,Fannouncement, that could still be
OL,13,FTuesday rather than Monday.
