OL,3,CPeston: Starmer could announce delayed
OL,4,Cdeparture to stay in post until
OL,5,CSeptember
OL,7,FOn whether there should be a formal
OL,8,Fleadership contest or an uncontested
OL,9,Fcoronation of Andy Burnham, I am told
OL,10,Fthe mood of MPs is polarised, but the
OL,11,Fmajority would prefer "the men and
OL,12,Fwomen in grey suits" to fix it for
OL,13,FBurnham, without a potentially
OL,14,Ffractious completion.
OL,16,FApart from anything else, even close
OL,17,Ffriends of Burnham say he is not yet
OL,18,Fready to govern.
OL,26,@sD@WOUtD@TO]
