PN,31504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1782118104
OL,3,CPeston: Starmer could announce delayed
OL,4,Cdeparture to stay in post until
OL,5,CSeptember
OL,7,F"He definitely needs time to work out
OL,8,Fhis team and programme," says an ally
OL,9,Fof his.
OL,11,FSo Starmer would be doing Burnham a
OL,12,Ffavour by staying in post another
OL,13,Fthree months - though he would do
OL,14,FBurnham a favour through gritted teeth
OL,15,Fthat would risk them falling out.
OL,17,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,18,Four political experts are across all
OL,19,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,20,Fto the latest episode below...
